==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Insulator
<hw>In"su*la`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who, or that which, insulates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Elec. & Thermotics)</fld> <def>A substance or
object that insulates; a nonconductor; <as>as, polyurethane foam is a
popular thermal <ex>insulator</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Insulite</ent>⟦br⟧
